WEBVTT

00:00:01.667 --> 00:00:06.059
Ebony Roberts: I remember
watching my father raise the pistol

00:00:06.083 --> 00:00:07.333
to my mother's head.

00:00:08.083 --> 00:00:11.643
She pleaded with him to put the gun down,

00:00:11.667 --> 00:00:12.917
but he ignored her.

00:00:14.500 --> 00:00:18.143
When she bolted toward the door,
he followed close behind

00:00:18.167 --> 00:00:21.917
and once outside,
he fired one single shot.

00:00:22.958 --> 00:00:24.208
I was 12.

00:00:25.000 --> 00:00:27.875
I remember this moment frame by frame.

00:00:28.667 --> 00:00:30.458
I remember feeling numb.